{"tid":511443,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"正式辭工轉做職賭","createTime":"2017-12-27T13:40:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T13:21:04.000Z","uid":98698,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"34ad74c4b12025f92e2dac7b651c7adbca1e85f7","tid":511443,"uid":98698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T13:40:22.000Z","msg":"近幾年日日打一份牛工<br />\n早起晚歸<br />\n先揾得2皮<br />\n每日受老世氣<br />\n同事又成日西口西面<br />\n因為番份垃圾工佔用左我大量時間<br />\n冇時間去溝女 約朋友等等<br />\n連同屋企人食飯既時間都冇左<br />\n<br />\n今次我考慮左好耐<br />\n今朝終於去辭左工<br />\n今日正式開始做全職賭徒<br />\n我覺得我有能力去靠賭揾好多 <br />\n而且生活就冇以前咁有限制<br />\n<br />\n條路自己簡<br />\n仆街唔會喊<br />\n<br />\n今日入左一萬本金起手<br />\n目標每日賺5000-10000<br />\n月薪希望做到15萬左右<br />\n<br />\n我每日投注會紀錄係telegram channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/Bettingtrip\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FBettingtrip&d=uc8ygWNqnQvFNSsWOWl2CpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=7e0a716e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/Bettingtrip</a><br />\n<br />\n希望如果有巴打都諗住靠賭既可以參考我幾個月再決定"},{"pid":"d01cb75692d0f3cf58817955cefc2a1508f319fd","tid":511443,"uid":922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T13:41:49.000Z","msg":"何必呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc2d6b87766cd366b67fa795d7db8c26f2892e55","tid":511443,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T13:43:05.000Z","msg":"勇氣"},{"pid":"9064c713a985ae43375f7bca8374e3877e57aa22","tid":511443,"uid":98698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T13:43:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>何必呢[img]assets/faces/xm/clown.png[/img]</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  對番工絕望"},{"pid":"eaf5439811472ec2ba34ba21a2b6353ae8b6dba2","tid":511443,"uid":108090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T13:43:57.000Z","msg":"單刀直入<br />\n幾錢入會?"},{"pid":"bb321576d9cdb7be39b7f30baae22452d0372836","tid":511443,"uid":157128,"like":0,"dislike":1,"s